data.description: **2.625% VA Assumable Loan available at 85% to qualified VA buyers.** Built to impress custom Sherwood Estates home located inside Cookeville City limits just 1 mile from TTU, & only 1 hour from Nashville! Featuring 5272 sq. ft of luxurious living space on 1.7+/- acres, this 7 BR/6 BA offers endless entertaining opportunities and includes all the amenities of upscale living: Private courtyard, security and intercom system throughout, gourmet eat-in kitchen w/ adjacent formal dining area, sun room, expansive living room w/ fireplace & wet bar, main level master suite w/ tray ceiling, fireplace, & jacuzzi tub en suite. Outdoor paradise consists of mature landscaping, salt water pool, playset, fire pit, walking bridge & seating area next to koi pond with fountain, gazebo, swing, wisteria covered patio, and irrigation/sprinkler system already in place. Pool house features additional kitchen, bath, laundry room, & fireplace.
